.Dd $Mdocdate: April 6 2026 $
.Dt SMTIIC 4 riscv64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm smtiic
.Nd SpacemiT I2C controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "smtiic* at fdt?"
.Cd "iic* at smtiic?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver supports the SpacemiT I2C controller for use with the
.Xr iic 4
framework.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr iic 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 7.9 .
.Sh AUTHORS
.An -nosplit
The
.Nm
driver was written by
.An Patrick Wildt Aq Mt patrick@blueri.se
and
.An Mark Kettenis Aq Mt kettenis@openbsd.org .
